questions.title: Why does glass taste like blood?
questions.qtext: I tried licking glass, and I didn't expect it to taste like anything, but I definitely taste blood now.

questions.title: Is coconut oil really ALL THAT?
questions.qtext: I don't buy it. Convince me.

questions.title: Why did myspace have to change???
questions.qtext: I spent so much time on my profile, and they just DELETED ALL OF IT!
